{"tid":2276003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁就一年...墨爾本手足有啲嘢想搞....","createTime":"2020-11-07T14:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T06:29:33.000Z","uid":230293,"like":76,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa1012a93a2e2c5ffa3772c5a713759a62952a1","tid":2276003,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得上年11月8號發生左咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4skyaFp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4skyaFp.png&h=7e354700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-50302812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-50302812&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft298yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=b19fab0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-50302812&h=65dce1f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-50302812</a><br />\n<blockquote>香港因為《逃犯條例》引發的示威浪潮持續。一名大學生早前在示威現場墮樓受傷，之後傷重不治。消息傳出後，許多香港市民上街悼念，要求當地政府徹查事實真相。<br />\n香港伊利沙伯醫院星期五（11月8日）向BBC中文證實，周梓樂當天香港時間上午08:09宣告不治，但未能提供進一步信息。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n事過境遷<br />\n<br />\n聽日有幾個傻仔（應該唔係樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）會係澳洲墨爾本搞個展覽仔，目的係同番當地人講上年11月8號發生左咩事，仲會解釋埋 #SAVE12 係咩意思。 <br />\n<br />\n時間：2-6 PM<br />\n地點：墨爾本CBD（實際地點樓豬聽日會再update）<br />\n<br />\n係墨爾本既巴絲到時可以黎寫下連儂牆，見到我地傾下計都得，一齊食派克G排<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n係最絕望既關頭，我地越唔可以放棄。"},{"pid":"0075c7c09a79a94652166eba31195e013470622d","tid":2276003,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beade2423ec71ee0c9900f3127b7b841ea23b97a","tid":2276003,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"大家黎既最多樓豬開少幾日鳩post <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714c622cc8d68185625af051e29a1f97a6b59343","tid":2276003,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b47c2d83bcf08f8b4c9f590bf7503bcbfe84304a","tid":2276003,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:44:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d29fef9534c711da210bce2955ccaf8e72fe2aa0","tid":2276003,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:45:11.000Z","msg":"樓主正7頭 幾時找數？"},{"pid":"f054a95dc2e2d7188bff03ba452b5ef07acd8761","tid":2276003,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"維園唔見你喎"},{"pid":"e40c90991ac1265afbce341a341f16e3d97055b9","tid":2276003,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d29fef9534c711da210bce2955ccaf8e72fe2aa0","tid":2276003,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:45:11.000Z","msg":"樓主正7頭 幾時找數？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"星期二係維多利亞省入面個公園找左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ec317294f8e65309d0f459dc0cd7b2399c581c","tid":2276003,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e40c90991ac1265afbce341a341f16e3d97055b9","tid":2276003,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d29fef9534c711da210bce2955c